<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NCERT Class 9 Science: Cell Study Companion</title>
    <style>
        /* ───────────── RESET & BASE ───────────── */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            overscroll-behavior: none;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #ebf3ee;
            color: #1e2b2a;
            line-height: 1.75;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .app-wrap {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100dvh;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 0;
            box-shadow: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            animation: appIn 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
        }
        @keyframes appIn {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.98); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* ───────────── HEADER ───────────── */
        .app-header {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #0f5132, #1a7a4a);
            padding: 18px 28px;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #a8d5ba;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .app-header h1 {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .app-header h1 small {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            opacity: 0.88;
            margin-left: 4px;
        }
        .nav-badge {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
            padding: 6px 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
            color: #fff;
            transition: background 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
        }
        button.nav-badge:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.32);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        button.nav-badge:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        /* ───────────── NAV TABS ───────────── */
        .section-tabs {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 4px;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            background: #f8fbf9;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dae8e0;
            max-height: 140px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .section-tabs button {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #2d4a40;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), color 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1), box-shadow 0.25s ease;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .section-tabs button:hover {
            background: #d4e8de;
            color: #0f5132;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .section-tabs button:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }
        .section-tabs button.active {
            background: #0f5132;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.25);
            animation: tabPop 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
        }
        @keyframes tabPop {
            0% { transform: scale(0.88); }
            60% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* ───────────── PAGE CONTAINER ───────────── */
        .page-container {
            padding: 20px 28px 32px;
            flex: 1 1 auto;
            overflow-y: auto;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        .page {
            display: none;
        }
        .page.active {
            display: block;
            animation: pageIn 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
        }
        .page.active .content-card {
            animation: fadeUp 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
        }
        .page.active .content-card:nth-of-type(1) { animation-delay: 0.04s; }
        .page.active .content-card:nth-of-type(2) { animation-delay: 0.11s; }
        .page.active .content-card:nth-of-type(3) { animation-delay: 0.18s; }
        .page.active .content-card:nth-of-type(4) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
        .page.active .content-card:nth-of-type(n+5) { animation-delay: 0.30s; }
        @keyframes pageIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(14px) scale(0.99);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
            }
        }
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(22px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* ───────────── CONTENT CARDS ───────────── */
        .content-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 24px 28px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.07);
            border: 1px solid #eaf3ee;
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .content-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.12);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .content-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f5132;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .content-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a5c3e;
            margin: 18px 0 8px;
        }
        .content-card h4 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f6b48;
            margin: 14px 0 6px;
        }
        .content-card p {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #253b34;
        }
        .content-card ul,
        .content-card ol {
            padding-left: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .content-card li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        /* ── analogy box ── */
        .analogy-box {
            background: #eaf5ef;
            border-left: 5px solid #198754;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin: 16px 0 20px;
        }
        .analogy-box strong {
            color: #0f5132;
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .analogy-box p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            color: #1a3d32;
        }

        /* ── listen btn ── */
        .listen-btn {
            background: #0f5132;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .listen-btn {
            transition: background 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1), box-shadow 0.25s ease;
        }
        .listen-btn:hover {
            background: #1a6e44;
            transform: scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.25);
        }
        .listen-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.96);
        }

        /* ── tables ── */
        .table-wrap {
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 16px 0 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #dae8e0;
        }
        .table-wrap table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
        }
        .table-wrap th {
            background: #0f5132;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .table-wrap td {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e4efe8;
            background: #fafffc;
        }
        .table-wrap tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .table-wrap tr:hover td {
            background: #f2faf5;
        }

        /* ── nav buttons ── */
        .nav-controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 28px 0 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .nav-controls button {
            background: #f0f7f3;
            border: 2px solid #d4e8de;
            padding: 10px 28px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #0f5132;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .nav-controls button:hover {
            background: #0f5132;
            border-color: #0f5132;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.20);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .nav-controls button:active {
            transform: scale(0.96);
        }
        .nav-controls button:disabled {
            opacity: 0.3;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .nav-controls .page-indicator {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #4d6b5f;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* ── Osmosis simulator ── */
        .osmosis-sim {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            background: #f4faf7;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 24px 20px 20px;
            margin: 18px 0 10px;
            border: 1px solid #cde0d6;
        }
        .osmosis-sim .cell-visual {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .osmosis-sim .cell-box {
            width: 140px;
            height: 140px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #d4e8de;
            border: 4px solid #0f5132;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f5132;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.1);
        }
        .osmosis-sim .cell-box .inner {
            transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
            width: 70%;
            height: 70%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #b8d9c8;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0a3d28;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.15);
        }
        .osmosis-sim .sim-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }
        .osmosis-sim .sim-btns button {
            padding: 8px 22px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            border: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            background: #e4efe8;
            color: #0f5132;
        }
        .osmosis-sim .sim-btns button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.04);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(15, 81, 50, 0.15);
        }
        .osmosis-sim .sim-btns button.hypo {
            background: #a8d5ba;
            color: #0a3d28;
        }
        .osmosis-sim .sim-btns button.iso {
            background: #cde0d6;
            color: #0f5132;
        }
        .osmosis-sim .sim-btns button.hyper {
            background: #f0c8c8;
            color: #6b2e2e;
        }
        .osmosis-sim .sim-label {
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1a4d3a;
            min-height: 1.6em;
        }

        /* ── SVG container ── */
        .svg-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 16px 0 10px;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #fafffc;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #e4efe8;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .svg-container svg {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% {
                opacity: 0.6;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 0.6;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0px);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-6px);
            }
        }
        @keyframes draw-line {
            to {
                stroke-dashoffset: 0;
            }
        }
        @keyframes glow {
            0%,
            100% {
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0 2px #198754);
            }
            50% {
                filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #0f5132);
            }
        }
        @keyframes move-dot {
            0% {
                transform: translate(0, 0);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            10% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            90% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translate(var(--tx), var(--ty));
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }
        @keyframes spin-slow {
            to {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }
        .pulse {
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        .float {
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .glow {
            animation: glow 2s infinite;
        }
        .bounce {
            animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;
        }

        /* connector line style (no arrowheads — plain lines) */
        .arrow-path {
            fill: none;
            stroke: #0f5132;
            stroke-width: 2;
            marker-end: none;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-dasharray: 220;
            stroke-dashoffset: 220;
            animation: draw-line 1.1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.25s;
        }
        .arrow-path-light {
            fill: none;
            stroke: #198754;
            stroke-width: 1.8;
            stroke-dasharray: 4 3;
            marker-end: none;
            stroke-linecap: round;
        }

        /* ── Quiz ── */
        .quiz-item {
            background: #f8fbf9;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 18px 22px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #dae8e0;
        }
        .quiz-item .q-text {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f5132;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .quiz-item .options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .quiz-item .options label {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #dae8e0;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.15s;
        }
        .quiz-item .options label:hover {
            border-color: #198754;
            background: #f2faf5;
        }
        .quiz-item .options input[type="radio"] {
            accent-color: #0f5132;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
        }
        .quiz-item .feedback {
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: none;
        }
        .quiz-item .feedback.show {
            display: block;
        }
        .quiz-item .feedback.correct {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #0a4a2a;
            border-left: 5px solid #198754;
        }
        .quiz-item .feedback.incorrect {
            background: #f8dddd;
            color: #6b2e2e;
            border-left: 5px solid #d9534f;
        }
        .quiz-score {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f5132;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px;
            background: #eaf5ef;
            border-radius: 40px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* ── responsive ── */
        @media (max-width: 700px) {
            .app-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 8px;
                padding: 18px 18px 14px;
            }
            .app-header h1 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .page-container {
                padding: 14px 14px 8px;
            }
            .content-card {
                padding: 18px 16px;
            }
            .section-tabs {
                padding: 10px 12px 4px;
                gap: 2px;
            }
            .section-tabs button {
                font-size: 0.7rem;
                padding: 4px 10px;
            }
            .nav-controls {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
            }
            .nav-controls button {
                justify-content: center;
                padding: 10px 16px;
            }
            .osmosis-sim .cell-box {
                width: 110px;
                height: 110px;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 450px) {
            .app-header h1 {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .content-card h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            .content-card {
                padding: 14px 12px;
            }
            .quiz-item {
                padding: 14px 12px;
            }
        }

        .highlight {
            background: #f0faf4;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #0f5132;
        }
        .mt-8 {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .mt-16 {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .mb-8 {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #d4e8de;
            color: #0f5132;
            padding: 2px 14px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="app-wrap">

        <!-- ─── HEADER ─── -->
        <header class="app-header">
            <h1>
                🌱 Cell Study Companion
                <small>NCERT Class 9 · Science</small>
            </h1>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <span class="nav-badge">📘 Chapter 2 · The Fundamental Unit of Life</span>
                <button id="fullscreenBtn" class="nav-badge" style="cursor:pointer; border:none; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;" onclick="toggleFullscreen()">⛶ Full Screen</button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- ─── TAB NAV ─── -->
        <nav class="section-tabs" id="tabNav">
            <button class="active" data-page="page-dashboard">🏠 Dashboard</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.1">2.1 Cells</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.1.1">2.1.1 Shape</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.2">2.2 Organisation</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.2.1">2.2.1 Membrane</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.2.2">2.2.2 Cell Wall</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.2.3">2.2.3 Nucleus</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.3">2.3 Organelles</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.3.1">2.3.1 ER</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.3.2">2.3.2 Golgi</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.3.3">2.3.3 Lysosomes</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.3.4">2.3.4 Mitochondria</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.3.5">2.3.5 Plastids</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.3.6">2.3.6 Vacuoles</button>
            <button data-page="page-2.4">2.4 Division</button>
            <button data-page="page-cancer">⚠️ Cancer</button>
            <button data-page="page-exam">📝 Exam</button>
        </nav>

        <!-- ─── PAGE CONTAINER ─── -->
        <div class="page-container" id="pageContainer">

            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <!-- DASHBOARD -->
            <!-- ============================================================ -->
            <section class="page active" id="page-dashboard">
                <div class="content-card">
                    <h2>🧬 Welcome to the Cell Study Companion</h2>
                    <p><strong>Class 9 · NCERT Science · Chapter 2: The Fundamental Unit of Life</strong></p>
                    <p>Every living thing — from the tiniest bacterium to the largest whale — is made of <span class="highlight">cells</span>. Cells are the tiny <strong>building blocks</strong> of life. In this companion, we'll explore everything about cells: what they're made of, how they work, and how they divide.</p>
                    <div class="analogy-box">
                        <strong>💡 Real-Life Analogy</strong>
                        <p>Think of your body like a huge building made of bricks. Each tiny brick is a <strong>cell</strong>. Alone, a brick is simple, but millions of bricks together make the whole building. Your body has trillions of cells working together!</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Animated Cell Banner -->
                    <div class="svg-container">
                        <svg width="500" height="120" viewBox="0 0 500 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <rect width="500" height="120" rx="16" fill="#eaf5ef" />
                            <circle cx="100" cy="60" r="45" fill="#d4e8de" stroke="#0f5132" stroke-width="3">
                                <animate attributeName="r" values="45;48;45" dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                            </circle>
                            <circle cx="100" cy="60" r="22" fill="#c0dccd" stroke="#198754" stroke-width="2">
                                <animate attributeName="r" values="22;24;22" dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
