                    <h2>2.1.1 Cell Shape, Size, and Diversity</h2>
                    <p>Cells come in many shapes and sizes, depending on the job they do. Most are microscopic (measured in <strong>micrometres</strong> — millionths of a metre), but some can be surprisingly large.</p>

                    <h3>🧫 Organisms by Cell Count</h3>
