                    <h2>2.4 Cell Division</h2>
                    <p>Cells divide to grow, repair, and reproduce. There are two main types:</p>

                    <h3>🧬 Mitosis — Growth &amp; Repair</h3>
                    <p>1 parent cell splits into <strong>2 identical daughter cells</strong>. Chromosome number stays the same. Used for growth and repairing damaged tissues.</p>
                    <div class="analogy-box">
